<B><FONT FACE="Osaka"><P ALIGN="CENTER">The Software for assessing the body image disturbance</P>
</B><H3>Description:</H3>
<P>BodyImage is the software for the study of the body image. The software uses the image distorting technique to assess the body size estimation. The images used in this program can be captured by digital camera or scanner. It displays the image on the computer display, and it uses the keyboard or a mouse to adjust the width of the image. The response data are recorded as an ASCII file. There is no need for any other devices. <BR>
  </P>
